      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ROSIE'S CHATTER (7) has been without a win for a while, the latest jumping from an outside draw when fourth (26.34) at this track in a Restricted WIN H. Form here sound including two wins. Tough to beat if on-song. PRINCE VALHALLA (8) drifted back from wide but charged home to hit the frame when 1.3 lengths from the winner (26.30) at this track in Grade 5. Is yet to miss the placings from this draw, including two wins, from six starts. Must be included in calculations. CARTMAN (2) was out of the placings last time but shapes well for this on his sharp win the start prior, getting around this track over 400m in 22.68. Expecting another bold showing. ROWDY'S BEAST (1) raced handy last time and scored. Hard to beat again.",
